SUMMARY:TTMTIN — Virtual Investor Call
DESCRIPTION:Series of virtual investor calls/meetings. Electronic presentation with voiceover will be made available. Standard Chartered Bank coordinating marketing logistics.\nIssuer: JAGUAR LAND ROVER AUTOMOTIVE (TTMTIN)\nRoadshow: https://dealroadshow.com/e/JLR_2026 | Entry Code: JLR_2026 | URL: https://dealroadshow.com\n\nDeal context:\nJaguar Land Rover Automotive plc (TTMTIN)\, rated Ba1 (Negative) / BBB- (Negative) and a wholly-owned subsidiary of Tata Motors Passenger Vehicles Limited\, has mandated Citigroup\, HSBC\, J.P. Morgan\, MUFG\, NatWest\, and Standard Chartered Bank as Joint Active Bookrunners to arrange virtual investor calls on 10 March 2026 ahead of a potential USD dual-tranche benchmark 144A/Reg S senior unsecured transaction across 3-year and 5-year tenors. The deal is guaranteed by Jaguar Land Rover Limited and Jaguar Land Rover Holdings Limited\, with Standard Chartered Bank coordinating marketing logistics. No pricing terms have been disclosed at this mandate stage\, and the transaction remains subject to market conditions.
LOCATION:Conference Call
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR